item.title: How do you change text on log out screen
item.dc:creator: @The_Outsider The Outsider
item.description:
@The_Outsider wrote:

All I know, is it should either be in the ActionSender, PlayerAssistant or Client class, otherwise you’ll have to add the method yourself, find the line numbers for the logout interface and edit them accordingly… it is server side though.

Edit:

Here’s the line numbers:

2450 = When you have finished playing 2451 = RuneScape, always use the 2452 = button below to logout safely. 2458 = Click here to logout
